text: hello I'm Rena fogal Chief technology
officer of Amazon and I'm proud to
announce the AWS Community HERO program
Community heroes are enthusiasts who
have gone above and beyond to make
significant contributions to the cloud
community and have taken the next step
to share that expertise with others
heroes are passionate about Cloud
technology engaging with others on Q&A
social sites blogging about it and
organizing community events our initial
group of Heroes includes many people
that you will surely recognize Eric
Hammond from alistic Peter sowow from
answers for AWS Ben wayy from Ani
Valentino F longi from atro Jeremy
edberg from Netflix and former from
Reddit and Aden cockroft former Netflix
and our B Ventures I applaud all these
individuals who have made significant
contributions to the technical community
and look forward to seeing all of them
in Las Vegas at the 2014 reinvent AWS
user conference we look forward to
announcing more Community Heroes soon
and until then thank you to everyone who
continues to contribute to the ads
community
